}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f6fcf234ab9b8f4eb0d3d1e970cb4a2d>.
<#f6fcf234ab9b8f4eb0d3d1e970cb4a2d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
