<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2ef48b70-7d1f-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__83081.
_:b0__83081 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.23 69.08,24.14 69.08,24.14 55.02,11.23 55.02,11.23 69.08))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
